  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT MY NEW GAME:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/9b396dd83f01d1b41ca2515e0c8a6e32.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=84 /></span><br><br>You've lost your cats. Go find them. <br><br>Find The Cat is a short puzzle platformer in which you have to find and collect colored cats to bring them back home<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is meant to be short and simple, with elements from puzzle platformers. There are currently 4 main levels in the game. Each one ending with you getting a cat. Pink, Blue, Turquoise and Green.<br>You have to trigger buttons to activate certain mechanisms to progress further. As well as jump on platforms and ledges.<br><br>The game autosaves at some points during the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><br>- Cats.<br>- a minimalistic abstract environmental art.<br>- Some puzzle and platformer elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/9b396dd83f01d1b41ca2515e0c8a6e32.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=84 /></span><br><br>You've lost your cats. Go find them. <br><br>Find The Cat is a short puzzle platformer in which you have to find and collect colored cats to bring them back home<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/8fc26d1b247d7a2f526a725bc8fead61.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is meant to be short and simple, with elements from puzzle platformers. There are currently 4 main levels in the game. Each one ending with you getting a cat. Pink, Blue, Turquoise and Green.<br>You have to trigger buttons to activate certain mechanisms to progress further. As well as jump on platforms and ledges.<br><br>The game autosaves at some points during the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/00cdec66b104dcbccf48fb1c16763dcd.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><br>- Cats.<br>- a minimalistic abstract environmental art.<br>- Some puzzle and platformer elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.poster.avif?t=1660822023\" width=580 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.webm?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814520/extras/ea8cb3268b62c9afcae2600bc312d2a9.mp4?t=1660822023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
